{"TopicId":26162,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Show off your flags MEGATHREAD","CreatedByName":"geb","CreatedById":5399,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-09T15:45:46Z","PageNum":41,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"draeath","CreatedById":25709,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-19T13:19:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThank you, Archer! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E (also, nice sig)\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESo. Do flags -have- to be 256x160? I would hope (assume even) that the engine should have no problems scaling an image down so long as it has the same aspect ratio (and is power-of-two). Might have to play with that...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EObviously you don\u0027t want to go crazy, but 256x160 seems crazy-small for a texture that should only exist in RAM once!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEDIT: have another! (\u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frisky_Dingo\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Esource\u003C/a\u003E)\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.draeath.net/linked-on-forums/kerbal/welcome-to-youre-doom_256x160.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.draeath.net/linked-on-forums/kerbal/welcome-to-youre-doom_256x160.png\u0022 alt=\u0022welcome-to-youre-doom_256x160.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-07-19T13:40:30Z\u0022 title=\u002207/19/2013 01:40  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 19, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by draeath\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Eadding a new flag\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"allmappedout","CreatedById":57281,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-19T15:08:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022draeath\u0022 data-cite=\u0022draeath\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EThank you, Archer! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E (also, nice sig)\u003Cp\u003ESo. Do flags -have- to be 256x160? I would hope (assume even) that the engine should have no problems scaling an image down so long as it has the same aspect ratio (and is power-of-two). Might have to play with that...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EObviously you don\u0027t want to go crazy, but 256x160 seems crazy-small for a texture that should only exist in RAM once!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEDIT: have another! (\u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frisky_Dingo\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Esource\u003C/a\u003E)\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.draeath.net/linked-on-forums/kerbal/welcome-to-youre-doom_256x160.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.draeath.net/linked-on-forums/kerbal/welcome-to-youre-doom_256x160.png\u0022 alt=\u0022welcome-to-youre-doom_256x160.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYES YES YES. Whilst you\u0027re at it, can you get Cat Party on my phone?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eedit: I vaguely remember the devs saying that it had to be that dimension, but hey, it\u0027s surely worth playing about with. But then again, the benefit of getting the game to scale it down vs doing it yourself are negligible..\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-07-19T15:10:57Z\u0022 title=\u002207/19/2013 03:10  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 19, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by allmappedout\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"draeath","CreatedById":25709,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-19T15:21:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EParts can define a surface to render the flag on. That part might be much larger than you usually see the flag drawn on. Sure, it will be mipmapped, but raising the texture resolution can help you keep crisp lines.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"eran100","CreatedById":17678,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-19T16:09:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Brotoro\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Brotoro\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EMeanwhile, in a nearby universe...\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/ntqB47c.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022ntqB47c.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHow did you....\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HeadHunter67","CreatedById":74121,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-19T16:23:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHere is the flag for my space agency, Kerbal Rocket And Space Headquarters (KRASH):\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v725/HidaOkami/KRASHflag2_zpsb464ca7a.png\u0022 alt=\u0022KRASHflag2_zpsb464ca7a.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt used to have a black star field background, it looked nice as a picture but that didn\u0027t work so well in the game. So I went with the gray \u0022static\u0022 background because I imagine that\u0027s what the viewers at home would be seeing after that \u0022landing\u0022. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"eran100","CreatedById":17678,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-19T16:27:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ECan someone makes several modefications to this flag \u003Ca href=\u0022https://encrypted-tbn1.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQg43tCt1-jcnwlIssEDmDsh5Gr0AZuhjM4MmuAZcJr-KgFvFJA\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://encrypted-tbn1.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQg43tCt1-jcnwlIssEDmDsh5Gr0AZuhjM4MmuAZcJr-KgFvFJA\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"draeath","CreatedById":25709,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-19T17:47:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ELike what?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"roosterr","CreatedById":61317,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-19T19:06:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EToo lazy to upload a photo of my flag to imgur, so see my sig below including my common plaque message \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Flixxbeatz","CreatedById":29991,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-19T19:15:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI think I\u0027ve already posted this here, hmm anyway...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/SklOTMf.png\u0022 alt=\u0022SklOTMf.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPlanning to make a new flag, without any texts in it. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"eran100","CreatedById":17678,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-19T20:59:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022draeath\u0022 data-cite=\u0022draeath\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ELike what?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIdk like adding a kerbal symbol inside or add a planet in it, be creative\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"draeath","CreatedById":25709,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-20T02:19:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.aspectofthehare.net/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/goodnews.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022goodnews.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EGreat news everyone!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EThe game accepts images larger than 256x160 without any issue.\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI selected and used a flag that was 800x500 (which is the same aspect ratio of 256x160 - in other words, 8:5) and it was both selectable \u003Cem\u003Eand\u003C/em\u003E it displayed at the space center!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"orangexception","CreatedById":72566,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-20T02:47:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/WlEkEyX.png\u0022 alt=\u0022WlEkEyX.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOrange Knot starts launches when 0.21 drops. Flags are getting ready for mass production.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sheherezade","CreatedById":70126,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-20T03:24:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/GBXXVof\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://imgur.com/GBXXVof\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ebecause I\u0027m a stone trekker.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Black Wyvern","CreatedById":47003,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-20T17:39:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v343/BlackWyvern/DRGN_zpsb42f0fd4.png\u0022 alt=\u0022DRGN_zpsb42f0fd4.png\u0022\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DBCreeper","CreatedById":64445,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-21T16:34:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI use this:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/Fuzbzkx.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022Fuzbzkx.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ricovandijk","CreatedById":71535,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-21T18:36:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EInhabitants of Diskworld and Kerbin have a not so very different look at the world actually \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i982.photobucket.com/albums/ae307/Ricovandijk/Kerbal/diskworld_zps07c514f4.png\u0022 alt=\u0022diskworld_zps07c514f4.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OUScooby","CreatedById":66208,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-21T19:03:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022draeath\u0022 data-cite=\u0022draeath\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.aspectofthehare.net/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/goodnews.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022goodnews.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003Cp\u003EGreat news everyone!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EThe game accepts images larger than 256x160 without any issue.\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI selected and used a flag that was 800x500 (which is the same aspect ratio of 256x160 - in other words, 8:5) and it was both selectable \u003Cem\u003Eand\u003C/em\u003E it displayed at the space center!\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EDid you end up with a larger flag, or did it scale down to 256x160?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Flixxbeatz","CreatedById":29991,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-21T19:07:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI think I will be using the thing in my signature as my latest flag. Too bad flags in-game are only one sided (meaning texts will flip on the other side). Or maybe my current avatar...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWhoever will guess the sources correctly first will get a cookie \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DBCreeper","CreatedById":64445,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-21T20:22:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Flixxbeatz\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Flixxbeatz\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E Whoever will guess the sources correctly first will get a cookie \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWhat your signatures sources? If that\u0027s the case then its Sword Art Online.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"spikeyhat09","CreatedById":39217,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-22T14:33:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/fmGJJW3.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022fmGJJW3.jpg\u0022\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"spikeyhat09","CreatedById":39217,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-22T15:10:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022draeath\u0022 data-cite=\u0022draeath\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.draeath.net/linked-on-forums/kerbal/welcome-to-youre-doom_256x160.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.draeath.net/linked-on-forums/kerbal/welcome-to-youre-doom_256x160.png\u0022 alt=\u0022welcome-to-youre-doom_256x160.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E*your\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://img196.yfrog.com/img196/1189/flamebait.gif\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E.gif\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-07-22T15:23:06Z\u0022 title=\u002207/22/2013 03:23  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 22, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by spikeyhat09\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"draeath","CreatedById":25709,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-22T17:04:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022spikeyhat09\u0022 data-cite=\u0022spikeyhat09\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E*your\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://img196.yfrog.com/img196/1189/flamebait.gif\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E.gif\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://video.adultswim.com/frisky-dingo/doom.html\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ENo, really?\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThat\u0027s the point.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022OUScooby\u0022 data-cite=\u0022OUScooby\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EDid you end up with a larger flag, or did it scale down to 256x160?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt\u0027s the same physical size, but I\u0027d put money down that it looks crisper up-close (or if/when you see flags on parts they will look nicer)\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027ve not planted a flag yet, so I can only go from the flagpole at the space center (which is distant, so it\u0027s not clear at all anyway)\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-07-22T17:08:36Z\u0022 title=\u002207/22/2013 05:08  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 22, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by draeath\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Eadditional\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"maniacc0","CreatedById":75284,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-22T18:07:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EMade up this little beauty last night... Red Hot Space Program (from Red Hot Chili Peppers, for those who don\u0027t know)...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i36.photobucket.com/albums/e28/maniacc0/RHSPFlagbig_zpsfe173f03.png\u0022 alt=\u0022RHSPFlagbig_zpsfe173f03.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"nAssailant","CreatedById":38911,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-23T03:39:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EMade this up for my new Space Corporation: Orbit Technologies. First launch scheduled when 0.21 finally comes out. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i714.photobucket.com/albums/ww148/J_Blast/OrbitFlagLarge.png\u0022 alt=\u0022OrbitFlagLarge.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-07-23T05:09:23Z\u0022 title=\u002207/23/2013 05:09  AM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 23, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by nAssailant\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Curly","CreatedById":75504,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-23T09:38:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/XefaGqB.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022XefaGqB.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis the first flag I\u0027ve made, this is also my first forum post!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHi everybody!\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}